# Working prompts, audit reports, and session runbooks (forward-only)
# Historical .md files committed before 2026-04-25 remain tracked.
# New .md files are local working materials by default.
# Wrap-ups go to Claude Project, code goes here.
*.md

# But keep these tracked
!README.md
!LICENSE.md
!LICENSE
!CHANGELOG.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CLAUDE.md
!SKILL.md

# And keep .md files inside these directories tracked
!src/**/*.md
!.claude/**/*.md
!supabase/**/*.md
!docs/**/*.md
